high_descs: Move past the island, turn right, move to the sink on the left, turn left, move to the sink
Pick up the knife on the counter in front of the sink
Turn around, move to the island, turn left, move to the fridge
Open the fridge, slice the watermelon, close the fridge
Turn left, move forward one tenth of a tile, turn right, open the fridge
Put the knife on the shelf next to the watermelon, close the fridge
Turn right, move one tenth of  a tile, turn left
Open the fridge, pick up a slice of watermelon, close the fridge
Turn around, move to the stove
Put the slice in the pan
Pick up the pan
Turn around, move to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the pan on the top shelf, close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of watermelon in a pan in the fridge

high_descs: Walk toward the dishwasher, then turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife laying on the counter in front of the sink.
Turn right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and slice the lettuce on the shelf, then close the refrigerator.
Turn to your left, the turn back to to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door, put the knife on the shelf next to the lettuce, and close the refrigerator door.
Turn to your right then turn back to face the refrigerator.
Take the end slice of the lettuce out of the refrigerator.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the other side of the room.
Put the slice of lettuce in the frying pan on the stove.
Pick up the frying pan.
Turn around and walk back to the refrigerator.
Put the pan with the slice of lettuce on the shelf in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with a slice of lettuce in it in the refrigerator.
